        返回:

      • executeForResults

        java.util.List<IEsptouchResult> executeForResults(int expectTaskResultCount)
                                           throws java.lang.RuntimeException
        Note: !!!Don't call the task at UI Main Thread or RuntimeException will be thrown Execute the Esptouch Task and return the result Smart Config v2.4 support the API It will be blocked until the client receive result count >= expectTaskResultCount. If it fail, it will return one fail result will be returned in the list. If it is cancelled while executing, if it has received some results, all of them will be returned in the list. if it hasn't received any results, one cancel result will be returned in the list.
        参数:
        expectTaskResultCount - the expect result count(if expectTaskResultCount <= 0, expectTaskResultCount = Integer.MAX_VALUE)
        返回:
        the list of IEsptouchResult
        抛出:
        java.lang.RuntimeException
